name: Super Moose Society
description: Evolve your Mini Moose into a Super Moose! Love Superheroes? Now you can turn your mini into one. Join us in the good fight against the evil mutants. I've said too much, but know there is a war brewing in the society. Will you stand with us? Need a Mini? Grab 2 OG Moose, send them on a 90 day side quest (stake), where they'll rescue and bring you back a FREE mini moose. Or mint a Super Box 1250 Available. 25 Ultra 1 of 1’s with over 200+ hand drawn traits!
